content:
The trip plan has been designed to satisfy all constraints and preferences as much as possible within the 14-day period. The stay lengths for Vienna and Santorini have been reduced from the desired 7 and 4 days to 5 and 3 days, respectively, to fit the total days while meeting the fixed requirements for Amsterdam and Lyon (3 days each, including the event days). The workshop in Amsterdam is attended on day 10 or 11, and the wedding in Lyon is attended on day 7 or 8, ensuring no conflict on day 9. All flights between cities are direct, as per the available connections.

The itinerary is as follows:
- Days 1-5: Vienna (5 days)
- Days 6-8: Lyon (3 days, wedding attended on day 7 or 8)
- Days 9-11: Amsterdam (3 days, workshop attended on day 10 or 11)
- Days 12-14: Santorini (3 days)

This plan uses direct flights: Vienna to Lyon (day 6), Lyon to Amsterdam (day 9), and Amsterdam to Santorini (day 12).

